---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy — StudyRoadmap™" description="StudyRoadmap™ privacy policy. We collect no personal data. Your exam choices stay on your device.">
  <Navbar />
  <main class="flex-1">
    <section class="bg-surface-50 dark:bg-surface-950 border-b border-surface-200 dark:border-surface-800">
      <div class="container-page py-14 text-center">
        <h1 class="heading-1 text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-50">Privacy Policy</h1>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="container-page py-14 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="card p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-6 text-sm text-surface-600 dark:text-surface-400 leading-relaxed">
        <p><strong class="text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100">Effective date:</strong> {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-IN', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
        <p>StudyRoadmap™ is built with privacy as a core principle. We collect <strong class="text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100">as little data as possible</strong>.</p>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">What We Collect</h2>
          <p>Nothing. We don't use analytics, tracking pixels, or third-party cookies. When you use StudyRoadmap™, we don't know who you are, what exam you're preparing for, or how long you're studying.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Local Storage</h2>
          <p>Your selected exam and duration preferences are stored in your browser's local storage for convenience. This data never leaves your device and is not transmitted to any server.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>We use <strong class="text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100">Vercel</strong> for hosting and <strong class="text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100">Cloudflare</strong> for DNS and SSL. These services may log basic request data (IP, user-agent) as part of their normal operations, governed by their own privacy policies.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>Our site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect any information from anyone under 13.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this policy occasionally. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Contact</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, reach out to us:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>
              <a href="mailto:contact@studyroadmap.in" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline dark:text-brand-400">
                contact@studyroadmap.in
              </a>
              — for privacy questions and data requests
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/studyroadmap/studyroadmap/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline dark:text-brand-400">
                Open a GitHub Issue
              </a>
              — for bug reports and feature suggestions
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
